3d19537d-6bbb-45a4-b39c-35631a6cf429.title: Aeonisig Raispher
3d19537d-6bbb-45a4-b39c-35631a6cf429.text:
Please only talk to the king if it's important. He has a
heavy burden to bear with the running of his kingdom.

options.text: How did you come to be an advisor to King Roald?

998baa31-ff21-4e04-bae2-dc7ff5e055e3.title: <player>
998baa31-ff21-4e04-bae2-dc7ff5e055e3.text: How did you come to be an advisor to King Roald?

3796faff-41ee-44c6-87d2-46782db189f5.title: Aeonisig Raispher
3796faff-41ee-44c6-87d2-46782db189f5.text:
The king of Misthalin, like any great leader, always
requires the best advice and the best advisors.

7ad380e1-e46e-4206-baa4-198d5fe46c5a.title: Aeonisig Raispher
7ad380e1-e46e-4206-baa4-198d5fe46c5a.text:
He very often summons occasional advisors to help him
in certain situations, but it was felt by the Church of
Saradomin that a full time advisor on religious matters
was needed.

8fff66a5-ec3b-44f1-b84a-131b15240de0.title: <player>
8fff66a5-ec3b-44f1-b84a-131b15240de0.text:
How come he doesn't have an advisor for any other
religious denominations?

d7b6c895-f30d-4336-b938-e20f4dcea522.title: Aeonisig Raispher
d7b6c895-f30d-4336-b938-e20f4dcea522.text:
Because I simply won't stand for it, that's why! Now,
enough of your impertinent questions. I have work to
do!

6eb77011-746c-4160-8662-1dfe5f812487.title: Aeonisig Raispher
6eb77011-746c-4160-8662-1dfe5f812487.text:
I took my religious and combat training in several parts
of the known world. I've also fought despicable beasts in
the Wilderness in Saradomin's name.

d98bb6d9-d214-434e-9a39-10a216d5bb08.title: Aeonisig Raispher
d98bb6d9-d214-434e-9a39-10a216d5bb08.text:
Needless to say I have great experience in the ways of
the world and am an invaluable aid to his lordship's
decision-making process.

6dbcf0a9-7a16-4f80-9b77-5dab902ca59a.title: Aeonisig Raispher
6dbcf0a9-7a16-4f80-9b77-5dab902ca59a.text:
My main function is to ensure that King Roald is
apprised of all options, especially those that favour the
righteous followers of Saradomin.

c514fa4c-6de5-4a6d-83db-a8550c6168c5.title: <player>
c514fa4c-6de5-4a6d-83db-a8550c6168c5.text:
But surely the king should be able to make his own
decisions on what's best for Misthalin?

a7ce0b25-1d7a-404f-8df2-889d4e286b01.title: Aeonisig Raispher
a7ce0b25-1d7a-404f-8df2-889d4e286b01.text:
What an interesting perspective you have! Totally
unworkable of course, but interesting nonetheless.

d8ac6fdd-2b94-405d-ac7a-709dec63130f.title: Aeonisig Raispher
d8ac6fdd-2b94-405d-ac7a-709dec63130f.text:
Apologies! Allow me to introduce myself. My name is
Aeonisig Raispher, special advisor to King Roald on
spiritual matters.

7be318a0-3186-4b59-b5e1-7d5df6a179fe.title: <player>
7be318a0-3186-4b59-b5e1-7d5df6a179fe.text:
Special advisor on spiritual matters? What does that
mean?

17ab207f-3c6e-4fcc-952a-a7df75ee1d63.title: Aeonisig Raispher
17ab207f-3c6e-4fcc-952a-a7df75ee1d63.text:
It means that some decisions the king has to make
might have unforeseen repercussions on the nation's
spiritual sensibilities.

ba2a5fd3-c2eb-4687-a7eb-44528ebe3f95.title: Aeonisig Raispher
ba2a5fd3-c2eb-4687-a7eb-44528ebe3f95.text:
My duty is to ensure that Saradominist ideals are not
stomped underfoot.
